Class IntersectionTile

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent

com.simulus.view.Tile
com.simulus.view.intersection.IntersectionTile
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class IntersectionTile extends Tile
An extension of Tile Allows storing of CustomPath and provides a reference to the intersection this tile belongs to.
